oneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2nd-november-2-of-141.jpg?w=700&amp;h=367 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Diwaan-i-aam</figcaption></figure>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_1880\" style=\"width: 1920px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1880\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2016/02/04/agra-the-fort/2nd-november-5-of-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2nd-november-5-of-14.jpg?w=1920&#038;h=579\" data-orig-size=\"1920,579\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;3.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Nabhoneel Majumdar&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS REBEL T3&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1446484367&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;800&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0005&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2nd November (5 of 14)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2nd-november-5-of-14.jpg?w=1920&#038;h=579?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2nd-november-5-of-14.jpg?w=1920&#038;h=579?w=700\" class=\" size-full wp-image-1880 aligncenter\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2nd-november-5-of-14.jpg?w=1920&#038;h=579\" alt=\"2nd November (5 of 14)\" width=\"1920\" height=\"579\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2nd-november-5-of-14.jpg 1920w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2nd-november-5-of-14.jpg?w=150&amp;h=45 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2nd-november-5-of-14.jpg?w=450&amp;h=136 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/